Package org.jicunit.framework

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JicUnitRunner
    A JUnit4 runner that delegates the actual execution of the test to be performed in a JEE container.
    JicUnitTestCase
    JUnit3 classes that inherits from this class will have there test executed in the container instead when the system property "jicunit.url" is set
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    RunInContainerWith
    When a class is annotated with @RunInContainerWith or extends a class annotated with @RunInContainerWith, JICUnit will invoke the class it references to run the tests in that class instead of the default runner in JUnit.
